'''''Amon Hen'' 118''' is the one-hundred-and-eighteenth issue of the [[The Tolkien Society]]'s bimonthly journal ''[[Amon Hen (journal)|Amon Hen]]'', published in November [[1992]].

** By: Susanne Stopfel

** By: Howard J. Bates
* Mathom

* Notices
